coordinate system
x : streamwise 
y : vertical 
z : spanwise left
                           
                         ^ ____                                                            
                       y |/   /            
                         |   /             
                        /|  /     __       
                  _____/ | /_____/ _/     x
                 /       |      /__/ ------------->
                 \_____    _______/        
                       \   \               
                        \ \ \              
                         \ \ \             
                          \_\_\            
                             \  z           
                              \| 
                           

Flow control spanwise quantity is g_i, defined as gamma_i/c_i,
i.e. local circulation divided by local chord length (= approximately local cl).

An inner product is defined on the linear space of all g_i vectors, defined as
g*g' = sum g_i*g'_i * dz_i

The equation to be satisfied locally is 
+-------------------------------------------------------+
|       rho * v * gamma = 1/2 * rho * v^2 * cl * c      |
+-------------------------------------------------------+

giving
+----------------------------+
|       g = v * cl / 2       |
+----------------------------+

cl = cl(alfa)
alfa = atan(vy/vx)
v = sqrt(vx^2 + vy^2)



